Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:23.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,《星際迷航: 新世界》前情提要\N{\rENG}Previously on Strange New Worlds...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.02,0:00:24.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,我現在要給你注射鎮定劑了\N{\rENG}I'm gonna give you a sedative now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.10,0:00:26.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,等你醒來 戈恩感染的問題就治好了\N{\rENG}And when you wake up, you will be Gorn-free.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:27.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,我還在這裡\N{\rENG}I'm still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:34.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,你能撐住的\N{\rENG}You are going to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.22,0:00:37.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,我可是艾麗卡·奧特加斯 無敵舵手\N{\rENG}I'm Erica Ortegas. I fly the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.84,0:00:40.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,伍中戀愛可能會導致一些複雜的問題\N{\rENG}Fraternization can lead to complications.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.94,0:00:43.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,就像我一直在告訴你的那樣 我只是需要點個人時間\N{\rENG}Like I've been trying to tell you, I just need some personal time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.20,0:00:44.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,遠離我的時間\N{\rENG}Away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.32,0:00:46.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,我正在考慮申請考古醫學研究員的職位\N{\rENG}About that fellowship, the archaeological medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.34,0:00:47.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,我得開始找人替補你了 是不是\N{\rENG}I'm going to have to replace you, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:48.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,失去你的念頭\N{\rENG}The thought of losing you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.96,0:00:50.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,深深困擾著我\N{\rENG}it affected me deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.28,0:00:52.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,但我還是要離開三個月\N{\rENG}I am still going away for three months
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.52,0:00:53.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,去和羅傑·科爾比一起學習\N{\rENG}to study with Roger Korby.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.88,0:00:55.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,等我回來 再看看我們的狀態吧\N{\rENG}When I get back, let's just see where we are then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.91,0:01:06.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,科學官個人日誌\N{\rENG}Science officer's personal log,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.52,0:01:08.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,星曆2251.7\N{\rENG}stardate 2251.7.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.94,0:01:11.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,在一號星站駐紮三個月後\N{\rENG}After a three-month billet at Starbase One,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.20,0:01:13.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們與戈恩人交戰造成的損傷\N{\rENG}the battle scars of our encounter
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.40,0:01:14.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,已經被全數修復\N{\rENG}with the Gorn are all but erased,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:17.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,這給我留下了很多時間去思考\N{\rENG}which has left me with a great deal of time to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.04,0:01:20.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,聯邦日百年慶典\N{\rENG}The Federation Day Centennial--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.64,0:01:22.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,慶祝星際聯邦成立\N{\rENG}the 100th anniversary of the founding of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.62,0:01:23.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,一百周年的日子\N{\rENG}the United Federation of Planets--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.94,0:01:25.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,還有三天就到了\N{\rENG}is just three days away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.96,0:01:29.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,派克艦長認為 為聯邦日組織一場慶典晚會\N{\rENG}Captain Pike believes that hosting a ceremonial gala for Federation Day 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:31.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,可以提振船員的士氣\N{\rENG}will improve morale among the crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.90,0:01:33.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,每一位船員的士氣\N{\rENG}All of the crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.84,0:01:37.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,查普爾護士結束外出 即將返艦\N{\rENG}Nurse Chapel is returning from her time away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.48,0:01:39.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,自從她離開去參加項目後 我們就再未聯繫過\N{\rENG}We have not spoken since she left for her fellowship.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.94,0:01:43.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,因此 我也有一個更加私人的理由\N{\rENG}As such, I have a more personal reason to prepare
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.32,0:01:44.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,來準備即將到來的慶典\N{\rENG}for the upcoming celebrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:11.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,放鬆你的肩膀\N{\rENG}Loosen up your shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:14.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,我的肩膀位置已經過精確測量\N{\rENG}My shoulder placement has been measured precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:15.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,又沒讓你去精確測量肩膀位置\N{\rENG}You're not supposed to measure them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.22,0:02:17.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,你該讓它們順其自然\N{\rENG}You're supposed to let them flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.58,0:02:19.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,就像這樣\N{\rENG}Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.94,0:02:32.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不明白\N{\rENG}I am confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.24,0:02:33.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不是已經按照你要求的參數\N{\rENG}Am I not already performing the movements to the 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.90,0:02:35.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,表演這些動作了嗎\N{\rENG}parameters you specified?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:37.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,你是 你只是太僵硬了\N{\rENG}Yes. You're just stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.78,0:02:38.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,就算是你 也僵得過分了\N{\rENG}Even for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.64,0:02:41.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,五 六 七 走\N{\rENG}Five, six, seven, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:43.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,請不要誤會我的意思\N{\rENG}Please do not take this the wrong way,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:45.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,你在這項活動上的天賦令人驚訝\N{\rENG}but your aptitude for this activity is surprising, 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.78,0:02:47.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,而且恕我直言\N{\rENG}and if I may say so,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.78,0:02:50.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,我認為這種願意嘗試新事物的態度非常適合你\N{\rENG}this openness to new life experiences suits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:53.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,有那麼一段時間\N{\rENG}There was a time 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:56.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,我最大的願望就是成為一位芭蕾舞的首席演員\N{\rENG}when I wanted nothing more than to be a prima ballerina.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.06,0:03:00.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,我猜測是戈恩人改變了你的想法\N{\rENG}I assume the Gorn changed that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.06,0:03:04.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,沒錯 我這輩子都在\N{\rENG}That's just it. I've spent my whole life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.65,0:03:06.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,等著他們捲土重來\N{\rENG}waiting for them to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.82,0:03:10.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,就像是我童年床底下的怪物\N{\rENG}My own personal nightmare under the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:12.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,然後他們真的回來了\N{\rENG}And here's the thing-- they came back
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:13.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,而我打敗了他們 就這樣\N{\rENG}and I beat them. Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:16.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是呢\N{\rENG}somehow
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.90,0:03:18.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,跟首席芭蕾舞演員比起來\N{\rENG}the Gorn are less ravenous
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:20.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩人都算溫順的\N{\rENG}than prima ballerinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:23.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,也許這就是為什麼瓦肯人原則上不跳舞\N{\rENG}Perhaps that is why Vulcans, as a rule, do not dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:26.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,看來就算是瓦肯人 也會為了特別的人而打破常規\N{\rENG}It seems some of you will defy that rule for the right person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:29.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,在人類文化中 久別重逢之際進行隆重的浪漫表達\N{\rENG}When humans reunite after a long absence, is it not tradition
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:31.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,難道不是傳統嗎\N{\rENG}to make a grand romantic gesture?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.64,0:03:35.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,史波克 我不想八卦\N{\rENG}Spock, I-I don't want to pry,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:37.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,但你和克莉絲汀不是決定\N{\rENG}but I thought you and Christine had 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:39.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,暫時分開 給彼此一點個人空間嗎\N{\rENG}decided to give each other some space.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:40.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,確實\N{\rENG}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.06,0:03:42.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,自從她離開去參加項目後 我們就再未聯繫過\N{\rENG}We have not spoken since she left for her fellowship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:45.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,不過大家都知道 距離最容易牽動人心\N{\rENG}But we all know what absence does to the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:47.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果沒{\fsp-45}了{\fsp-0}「心」將會是致命的\N{\rENG}The absence of a heart would be quite fatal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:50.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,不 史波克 這只是比喻 我是說\N{\rENG}No, Spock, it's an idiom, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.22,0:03:58.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,進取號呼叫史波克先生\N{\rENG}Enterprise to Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:01.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,你要我提醒你 那好 注意了\N{\rENG}You asked for a heads-up, so, heads up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.56,0:04:04.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,查普爾護士請求傳送許可了\N{\rENG}Transport clearance request from Nurse Chapel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:05.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,她來了 我先失陪了\N{\rENG}Please excuse me. She is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:18.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,挺帥啊 史波克先生\N{\rENG}Looking good, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:20.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,你怎麼在這\N{\rENG}Lieutenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.02,0:04:21.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,職責需要\N{\rENG}Just doing my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:23.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,查普爾在訪客名單上加了人\N{\rENG}Chapel added someone to the visitors list.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:24.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,有趣\N{\rENG}Curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.96,0:04:27.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,有點怪\N{\rENG}That's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:28.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,剛剛某個瞬間\N{\rENG}You know, for a wee moment there, I thought
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.96,0:04:30.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,我還以為我看到了一點異樣\N{\rENG}I saw a bit of strangeness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:32.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,什麼樣的異樣\N{\rENG}What sort of strangeness?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:34.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,只是個船體外的傳感器虛影\N{\rENG}Oh, just a sensor ghost outside the hull.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:35.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,但它現在不見了\N{\rENG}But it's gone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:37.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,沒啥值得看的 長官\N{\rENG}Nothing to see here, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:40.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,所有相關的掃描結果均處在正常範圍內\N{\rENG}All relevant scans appear to be within normal parameters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:43.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,斯考特中尉 傳送兩人上艦\N{\rENG}Two to beam aboard, Lieutenant Scott.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:52.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,史波克\N{\rENG}Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:54.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,克莉絲汀\N{\rENG}Christine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:58.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,這位是科爾比博士\N{\rENG}Uh, this is Dr. Korby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:05:00.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,-你的研究項目指導? -嗯哼\N{\rENG}- Your fellowship director? - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.84,0:05:02.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,科爾比博士 向您問好\N{\rENG}Greetings, Dr. Korby.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:03.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,你好你好 叫我羅傑就行\N{\rENG}How are you? Call me Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.84,0:05:05.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,我聽說了不少關於你的事 史波克\N{\rENG}I've, uh, heard a lot about you, Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:07.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,科爾比博士 我也讀過許多您\N{\rENG}Dr. Korby, I have read a considerable number
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:09.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,在考古醫學領域上的論文\N{\rENG}of your papers on archaeological medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:11.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,其實也沒那麼多\N{\rENG}Oh, sure, there aren't that many.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:14.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,一共有二百三十四篇 我說錯了嗎\N{\rENG}There are 234. Is that not accurate?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.76,0:05:17.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,沒錯 確實是這麼多\N{\rENG}It's actually exactly how many there are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.86,0:05:18.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,哇哦\N{\rENG}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.82,0:05:22.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,那是第一版{\fsp-30}的{\fsp0}《薩塔凡圖爾{\fsp-30}》嗎\N{\rENG}Is that a first edition of Saltavantur?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:24.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,可以看看嗎\N{\rENG}May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:27.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,這太不可思議了\N{\rENG}This is incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:29.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,光是這個雕刻設計肯定就能追溯到\N{\rENG}The engravings alone must date back to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:32.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,這是給克莉絲汀的禮物\N{\rENG}It is a gift for Christine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:34.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,哇\N{\rENG}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:39.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,總之 歡迎登艦 科爾比博士\N{\rENG}Well, welcome aboard, Dr. Korby.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:41.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,需要為你安排住宿嗎\N{\rENG}Will you be needing quarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:45.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,呃 不用了\N{\rENG}Uh, no, no, I'm, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:47.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,我有安排了\N{\rENG}I'm taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:49.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,他是來這裡\N{\rENG}He is here
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:52.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,和我一起參加百年慶典的\N{\rENG}to attend the centennial celebration with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:56.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,和你?\N{\rENG}With you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:03.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,科爾比博士是我的約會對象\N{\rENG}Dr. Korby is my date.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:07.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,厲害\N{\rENG}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:11.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}八英尺高的鬣蜥都沒能幹掉我\N{\rENG}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:12.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}你小子想打倒我 還遠著呢\N{\rENG}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:13.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,繼續啊 老弟\N{\rENG}Come on, baby boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:15.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}是想吃我一記重拳嗎\N{\rENG}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:17.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,你接不住我的全力重擊的\N{\rENG}You can't handle the haymaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:17.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,誰說的\N{\rENG}Who even says that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.84,0:08:19.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}誰說的不重要 你努力還擊就行了 我們繼續吧\N{\rENG}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.46,0:08:20.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}你真是個討厭鬼\N{\rENG}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:21.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}準備好吃拳頭吧\N{\rENG}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:27.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,別太得意 我可要打中了啊\N{\rENG}Don't get cocky, I'll land one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:35.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\rENG}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.18,0:08:37.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,我早就告訴過你把攝像機關掉\N{\rENG}I told you to turn that camera off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.88,0:08:38.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,我只是在做我的工作啊\N{\rENG}I'm just doing my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:39.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊 你的工作\N{\rENG}Yeah, your job
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.44,0:08:41.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,是拍攝星聯百年慶典的紀錄片\N{\rENG}is a documentary on the centennial gala,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.14,0:08:42.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,而不是拍攝我們訓練\N{\rENG}not this workout.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:43.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,我是一名專業的電影製作人\N{\rENG}I am a serious filmmaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.86,0:08:45.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,艾麗卡 可算找到你了\N{\rENG}Erica, ah, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.28,0:08:46.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,和你說件難以置信的事\N{\rENG}You are not going to believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.10,0:08:49.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,克莉絲汀帶了個男朋友回家\N{\rENG}Christine brought home a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:50.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,查普爾?\N{\rENG}Chapel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:51.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,我剛知道的時候和你一樣震驚\N{\rENG}I'm just as shocked as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.66,0:08:53.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\rENG}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.12,0:08:55.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,嗨 我是\N{\rENG}Hi. I'm, uh--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:08:56.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,重拳出擊\N{\rENG}Haymaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.63,0:09:00.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧 這是誰\N{\rENG}Okay, who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:02.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,這是我弟弟\N{\rENG}That's my little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:04.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,他從來就接不住拳頭\N{\rENG}Never could take a punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.76,0:09:06.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\rENG}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.66,0:09:08.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,我是妮歐塔\N{\rENG}I'm Nyota.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.54,0:09:13.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,行了 就快好了\N{\rENG}All right, almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.88,0:09:15.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,不急的 少尉\N{\rENG}Take your time, Ensign.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.48,0:09:17.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,百年慶典的準備工作那麼多\N{\rENG}With all the centennial preparations I have to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:19.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,這已經是我最接近度假的待遇了\N{\rENG}this is the closest thing to a vacation I'm gonna get.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.04,0:09:22.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,這就是最後一管了\N{\rENG}Well, this is the last one,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:24.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是我可以再抽幾管\N{\rENG}but I can take a bunch more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:26.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,說真的 一個人能需要多少血啊\N{\rENG}I mean, how much blood does a person really need?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:28.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,護士學校沒教這個嗎\N{\rENG}They didn't cover that in nursing school?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:30.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,我上課時候睡著了\N{\rENG}Oof, I fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.08,0:09:31.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,還很經常\N{\rENG}Like, a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.24,0:09:33.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,我挺喜歡你的 少尉\N{\rENG}I like you, Ensign.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.66,0:09:35.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,可是呢 現在查普爾護士回來了\N{\rENG}Well, now that Nurse Chapel is back,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.20,0:09:37.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,我的臨時任命期就結束了\N{\rENG}my temporary assignment is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:39.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,話別說的這麼絕對\N{\rENG}I wouldn't be so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:40.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,別這樣看著我\N{\rENG}Don't look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:42.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,去看你的直屬上司去\N{\rENG}Take it up with your direct supervisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.28,0:09:43.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,你猜對了\N{\rENG}Guilty as charged.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:45.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,我已經向星際艦隊醫療部提交了申請\N{\rENG}I put in a request with Starfleet Medical
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:46.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,希望把你的調任期限轉為永久\N{\rENG}to make your transfer permanent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:50.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,等等 別騙我啊 別最後告訴我只是惡作劇\N{\rENG}Wait, wait, please tell me this isn't a cruel joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:52.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們這最喜歡玩這種惡作劇了\N{\rENG}We are big on cruel jokes around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:54.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,等你第一次參加艦長的晚宴就知道了\N{\rENG}Just wait until your first formal Captain's Table.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:55.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,不過這次確實是認真的\N{\rENG}But in this case, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.54,0:09:58.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,很顯然 你上司不捨得讓你離開\N{\rENG}Apparently, he isn't ready to give you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:00.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,誠實地說 我們都不捨得看你離開 少尉\N{\rENG}Frankly, none of us are, Ensign.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.34,0:10:03.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\rENG}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.98,0:10:10.05,CHS,,0,0,0,,能有你在 巴特爾艦長真是幸運\N{\rENG}Captain Batel is lucky to have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:11.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,瑪麗恢復得怎麼樣了\N{\rENG}How's Marie doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.18,0:10:12.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,掃描結果顯示 \N{\rENG}Her scans show that 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.56,0:10:15.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩胚胎殘餘物質已經被她的身體完全吸收了\N{\rENG}the Gorn embryos have been fully reabsorbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:21.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,是你的血讓她的身體足夠強韌\N{\rENG}It was your blood that kept her body
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:24.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,才順利撐過了代謝吸收的過程\N{\rENG}strong enough to survive the metabolization process.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:27.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們只是處理了一些輕微的後遺症罷了\N{\rENG}All we're doing now is managing some minor aftereffects.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:29.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,我都習慣了她的存在了\N{\rENG}I've gotten used to having her on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.84,0:10:31.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,她要是走了我還真有點捨不得\N{\rENG}I'll be sorry to see her go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:33.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,要是如此 難過的肯定不止你一個\N{\rENG}I imagine you won't be the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:39.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,說真的\N{\rENG}I have literally
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.60,0:10:41.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,有些勳章我都不知道是為什麼頒的\N{\rENG}no idea what some of these medals are for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.46,0:10:44.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,而且我也不能全戴上 是吧\N{\rENG}And I can't wear all of them, or can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:46.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,挑著戴啊\N{\rENG}Pick one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:47.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,不行 要是只戴一個\N{\rENG}No. Because then I would insult 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.98,0:10:49.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,沒戴的那些人不就覺得我是在冒犯他們嗎\N{\rENG}whoever gave me the ones I'm not wearing and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:52.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,當一個你這麼優秀的艦長真不容易啊\N{\rENG}Must be hard being such an amazing captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:10:58.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,呃\N{\rENG}You, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:10:59.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,你是在物色自己的新座艦嗎\N{\rENG}shopping for a new starship?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:03.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,上將說了 要什麼樣的星艦由我來定\N{\rENG}Admiral April said I've got my pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:05.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,這兒有各式各樣的星艦可供選擇\N{\rENG}There are about a dozen commissions available.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.66,0:11:07.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,很好啊\N{\rENG}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:10.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,那你想要什麼樣的呢\N{\rENG}So, what are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.14,0:11:13.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,深空探索型\N{\rENG}Deep space exploration.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.18,0:11:16.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,但這樣的話我就見不到你了\N{\rENG}But then I never see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:18.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,或者短距離的外交郵輪\N{\rENG}Or short-range diplomatic courier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:21.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,但這樣我還是會見不到你\N{\rENG}But then I still never see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.06,0:11:29.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,我到現在都覺得像是在做夢\N{\rENG}It still doesn't feel totally real.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:31.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,我本該死了的\N{\rENG}I should be dead, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:32.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,我還活著只是僥天之幸\N{\rENG}I'm on borrowed time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.52,0:11:35.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,說到這個 我都明白的\N{\rENG}Well, you're preaching to the choir on that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.52,0:11:35.56,Note,,0,0,0,,* 這句話字面意思就是「向唱詩班布道」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.94,0:11:40.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,你這麼說我都能想像出來你在唱詩班的樣子了\N{\rENG}Now I'm just picturing you in a boys' choir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:43.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,其實我以前還真是教堂的侍童\N{\rENG}Actually, I was an altar boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:46.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,你是個艦長 你會找到你的船的\N{\rENG}You're a captain. You'll find your ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:48.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,我只是希望這個過程能慢一點\N{\rENG}I just wish it didn't have to be so soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:51.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,你想說什麼呢 艦長\N{\rENG}What are you asking me, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:56.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,實話說 我也不知道\N{\rENG}Frankly, I don't know. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:11:57.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,我只知道\N{\rENG}All I know is that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.74,0:11:59.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,我還沒準備好和你分別\N{\rENG}I'm not ready to let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:04.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,這就有點尷尬了\N{\rENG}Well, this is awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:08.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,不好意思\N{\rENG}Right, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:10.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,剛剛我說的太過分了\N{\rENG}It was too far. That...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:11.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,逗你的呢\N{\rENG}Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.34,0:12:13.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,我在想 等你和我搬到一起住之後\N{\rENG}I was just wondering what you're gonna do
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:15.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,你要怎麼辦\N{\rENG}when I move you into my quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:17.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,你那些護理頭髮的瓶瓶罐罐要放在哪\N{\rENG}Where will all your hair products go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.30,0:12:32.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\rENG}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:34.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,我把這個帶來了\N{\rENG}I-I brought this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:35.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,我覺得我應該還給你\N{\rENG}I thought you might want it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:37.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,這是給你的禮物\N{\rENG}It was a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:39.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,我何必要反悔\N{\rENG}Why would I not wish for you to have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.72,0:12:41.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,之前的事 很抱歉\N{\rENG}I'm sorry about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:45.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,我沒想讓你和羅傑的第一次見面那麼尷尬\N{\rENG}I didn't want you to meet Roger like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.08,0:12:46.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,你臉上那副驚訝的表情\N{\rENG}The look of surprise on your face
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:48.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,幾乎讓我覺得這次失誤值了\N{\rENG}was almost worth the misstep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:51.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,這對我來說也不容易\N{\rENG}This isn't easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.78,0:12:57.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,我能問你一個直白的問題嗎\N{\rENG}May I ask you a direct question?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:12:59.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,你哪次問的不直白了\N{\rENG}Never known you to be any different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.91,0:13:02.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,你說你不希望進入一段\N{\rENG}You expressed the desire to remain unattached,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,正式的關係\N{\rENG}free of commitment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:07.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,然而我卻帶了一個男朋友\N{\rENG}And then I bring my new boyfriend
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:08.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,回家過節\N{\rENG}home for the holidays.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:11.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\rENG}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:18.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,等我自己搞清楚了之後\N{\rENG}When I figure that out for myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.79,0:13:20.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,我發誓我會第一個\N{\rENG}I swear you will be the first person
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:22.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,向你解釋的\N{\rENG}that I explain it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:29.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,事實是 我自己也不知道\N{\rENG}The truth is, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.54,0:13:32.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,就這麼發生了\N{\rENG}It just is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:34.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,斯波克\N{\rENG}Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:36.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們還能做朋友嗎\N{\rENG}Are we gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:45.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們今晚在艦上的餐廳有雞尾酒會\N{\rENG}We're having cocktails in the Port Galley tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:47.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,希望你能來\N{\rENG}I hope you'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.93,0:14:00.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧 我就喝一杯 然後我就要回去訓練了\N{\rENG}Fine, one drink, then I have to go back and finish training.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:03.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,之前誰還教我龍舌蘭酒能當飯吃的來著\N{\rENG}Aren't you the one who taught me tequila is its own food group?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:05.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}來點龍舌蘭能讓你冷靜下來 伙計\N{\rENG}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:07.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,你知道她是我們的通訊官對吧\N{\rENG}You realize she's our communications officer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.44,0:14:09.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,她會的語言 有九百種了吧\N{\rENG}She speaks, like, 900 languages.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.46,0:14:11.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,煩人精姐姐語算是其中一種嗎\N{\rENG}Is "obnoxious big sister" one of 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:13.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,別勸她了 貝托 跟我一起去玩吧\N{\rENG}Let it go, Beto. You can hang with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.72,0:14:14.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,正合我意\N{\rENG}That seems like a plan to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:18.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,等一下 不對勁\N{\rENG}Wait one damn minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.82,0:14:20.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,你倆什麼情況\N{\rENG}This, you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.62,0:14:22.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,跟對方說話的語氣就像你們\N{\rENG}...talking to each other like you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:23.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,看對方的眼神也是 就像\N{\rENG}and looking at each other like you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:26.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,不行 這簡直一團亂麻 瘋了\N{\rENG}No. It's chaos, madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.58,0:14:27.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,你不放心把你最好的朋友交給我嗎\N{\rENG}You don't trust me with your best friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:29.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,你不放心把你的寶貝弟弟交給我嗎\N{\rENG}You don't trust me with your baby brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:34.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,行了行了 那我自己去訓練了\N{\rENG}Okay. Okay, I'll stay for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:35.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是你們不許當著我的面調情\N{\rENG}But there will be no more flirting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:38.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,絕對不許啊\N{\rENG}Literally none.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:39.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,科爾比博士\N{\rENG}So, Dr. Korby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:41.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,我是山姆 我得說 我非常敬佩\N{\rENG}Uh, Sam. I got to say, I'm a big fan
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.01,0:14:43.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,您在高等古代文明研究方面的貢獻\N{\rENG}of your work on advanced ancient cultures.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:46.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,報道說您最近的考古發掘是在瓦迪亞九號星\N{\rENG}I read that your latest dig was on Vadia Nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.14,0:14:46.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\rENG}Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.72,0:14:48.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,那您有爬過迦勒山嗎\N{\rENG}Uh, have you climbed Mount Caleb?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.64,0:14:50.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊 我們爬過了\N{\rENG}Uh, we did, actually. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:52.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,事實上 爬山的過程還挺浪漫的呢\N{\rENG}It was, it was pretty romantic, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:54.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,斯波克先生\N{\rENG}Uh, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.34,0:14:56.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,很高興你能來\N{\rENG}Glad you could join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:14:59.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,我的工作提早完成了\N{\rENG}I finished my work early.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.78,0:15:03.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,科爾比博士正要給我們講一個浪漫的故事呢\N{\rENG}Dr. Korby was just about to tell us a romantic story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.12,0:15:04.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,-噢 那還是別提了 -是啊\N{\rENG}- Oh, no,don't worry about it.- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:05.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,-要不改天吧 -你們肯定不想聽\N{\rENG}- Some other time. - You guys don't want to hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.77,0:15:06.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,-只是個超無聊的故事 -是啊\N{\rENG}- Bore the life out of you. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:08.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,我很樂意聆聽\N{\rENG}I would like to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.06,0:15:10.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,最近我正在學習關於浪漫的知識\N{\rENG}I have, of late, become a student of romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:13.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,忽然好渴\N{\rENG}Sudden thirst.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.34,0:15:15.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,貝托 跟我一起去拿些飲料來\N{\rENG}Beto, give me a hand with some drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:19.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧 是這樣的\N{\rENG}Okay. Um... Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.38,0:15:21.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,那是我小時候的事情了\N{\rENG}uh, when I was a little girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:23.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,每次我出門之前\N{\rENG}whenever I would go away on a trip--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:25.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,無論是去露營還是去學校\N{\rENG}to camp, to school--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.22,0:15:27.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,我媽媽都會對我說\N{\rENG}my mother would always say to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.22,0:15:30.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,「克麗絲 我希望你能找到屬於你的陽光」\N{\rENG}"Chrissy, I hope you find the sun..."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.48,0:15:34.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,「願你尋得屬於自己的日月星辰」\N{\rENG}"I hope you find the sun and the moon and the stars."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.06,0:15:35.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\rENG}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:39.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,結果到頭來 這句話成了她\N{\rENG}And they turned out to be the last words
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:41.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,對我說的最後一句話\N{\rENG}she ever said to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.02,0:15:43.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,然後\N{\rENG}And, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.32,0:15:45.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,是這樣 迦勒山剛好要高過太陽平面\N{\rENG}Mount Caleb actually happens to break the solar plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:48.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以太陽和月亮會同時出現\N{\rENG}So, um, the sun and the moon are visible at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:50.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,那天又是我媽媽的生日\N{\rENG}And it was my mother's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:53.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,我沒有把這事告訴過任何人\N{\rENG}And I didn't tell anybody
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:55.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,我一向如此\N{\rENG}'cause I never do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.04,0:15:58.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,可是他注意到我情緒低落\N{\rENG}Uh, but he just noticed that I was down and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:03.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,注意到這兩件事的關聯了\N{\rENG}remembered the story and put two and two together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:05.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們到達山頂的時候\N{\rENG}And when we got to the top...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.16,0:16:07.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,登上山頂之後\N{\rENG}When we got to the top,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.28,0:16:10.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,我向她展示了絕美的天空\N{\rENG}I showed her the stunning sky
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:14.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,然後送給她這個\N{\rENG}and gave her this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:17.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,提拉利安星鑽\N{\rENG}Tilaryan Star Gems.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:19.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,-這可是舉世罕見的珍寶 -沒錯\N{\rENG}- They're incredibly rare. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.82,0:16:22.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,然後他說\N{\rENG}And he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:24.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,「你好像很難過\N{\rENG}"You looked sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.61,0:16:28.65,CHS,tag,0,0,0,,所以我想要送給你日月星辰」\N{\rENG}I wanted to give you the sun and the moon and the stars."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:43.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,-祭酒來啦 -大家都來一杯\N{\rENG}- Libations. - Shots, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.12,0:16:44.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,-妙啊 -謝天謝地\N{\rENG}- Fun. - Thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.23,0:16:48.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,好酷的手鐲 哪裡來的\N{\rENG}Ooh, that's a cool bracelet. Where'd you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.82,0:17:07.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,晚上好\N{\rENG}Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.82,0:17:11.18,Note,,0,0,0,,* 假裝成瓦肯酒保的是特雷蘭 見《原初系列》1x18「哥索斯的侍從」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.16,0:17:10.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,準備好換一換口味了嗎\N{\rENG}Ready for a change?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.35,0:17:13.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,我從未知曉 艦上有一位瓦肯酒保\N{\rENG}I was not aware we had a Vulcan bartender.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.46,0:17:14.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,臨時調任\N{\rENG}Temporary posting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.83,0:17:16.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,路過而已\N{\rENG}Just passing through.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.92,0:17:20.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,那麼 要來一點不同 但是很讚的東西嗎\N{\rENG}So, something different but better?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.34,0:17:22.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,你一定想嚐嚐的東西\N{\rENG}Something you definitely want?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:25.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,嗯 可以接受\N{\rENG}Yes, that would be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.95,0:17:27.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\rENG}Fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.82,0:17:30.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,我正好有你想要的\N{\rENG}I have just the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.58,0:17:34.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,晃一晃酒杯 讓香氣散發出來\N{\rENG}Swirl it around. Brings out the aroma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:37.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,別喝得太急\N{\rENG}Don't drink it too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:38.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,會上頭哦\N{\rENG}It'll go right to your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:21.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,早上好啊\N{\rENG}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:29.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,早上好 你也是\N{\rENG}Good morning back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.01,0:18:35.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,今晚不能和我睡一起哦\N{\rENG}Tonight, no sleepover.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:40.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,婚禮當天見到自己的新娘 會倒霉的\N{\rENG}It is bad luck to see your bride on the day of your wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:51.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,科學官個人日誌\N{\rENG}Science Officer's personal log.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:54.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,星曆2251.7\N{\rENG}Stardate 2251.7.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:55.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,經過三個月的駐紮\N{\rENG}After a three-month billet,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.66,0:18:57.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們與戈恩人交戰造成的損傷\N{\rENG}the battle scars of our encounter with the Gorn
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.50,0:18:58.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,已經被全數修復\N{\rENG}are all but erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:01.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,在一號星際基地的停靠期間\N{\rENG}And while docked at Starbase One,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:04.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們的船員在為難得一遇的歡樂時刻做準備\N{\rENG}our crew prepares to celebrate a rare and joyous occasion,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.84,0:19:08.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,那就是我自己和查普爾護士的婚禮\N{\rENG}the wedding nuptials between myself and Nurse Chapel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.28,0:19:09.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,你的第一支舞絕對會驚艷四座\N{\rENG}Your first dance is going to be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.80,0:19:10.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,你進步很大\N{\rENG}You're improving.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.91,0:19:12.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,並非如此\N{\rENG}Untrue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.10,0:19:17.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,我從未理解 為什麼需要用欺騙\N{\rENG}I've never understood the need for deception
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:19.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,來緩和潛在的負面反應\N{\rENG}to smooth a potential negative reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:22.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,和你結婚怕是要享受囉\N{\rENG}You're just going to excel at marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:26.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,你結過婚嗎\N{\rENG}Have you ever been married?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:28.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,我嗎 絕對不可能\N{\rENG}Me? God no.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:30.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不是那種適合長期關係的人\N{\rENG}I'm not really the commitment type.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:34.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,我的童年經歷 讓我很難接受穩定的情感依賴\N{\rENG}My childhood didn't really set me up for a stable attachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:39.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是呢 一邊跑一邊朝後開槍\N{\rENG}Now, shooting backwards while running,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.18,0:19:40.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,我倒是很在行\N{\rENG}that I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.64,0:19:45.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,我必須說 你最近看起來輕鬆了許多\N{\rENG}Of late, I must say you have seemed lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.80,0:19:49.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,史波克 如果你現在還沒練好\N{\rENG}Spock, if you don't have it by now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.94,0:19:51.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,那就太晚了\N{\rENG}then it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.84,0:19:53.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 拉安\N{\rENG}Thank you, La'An.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.34,0:19:54.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,你一直是我很好的朋友\N{\rENG}You have been a good friend to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:57.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,我該去準備彩排了\N{\rENG}I must prepare for the rehearsal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:08.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,各就各位 我們還有很多要做呢\N{\rENG}Places, everyone! We have much to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:10.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,婚禮又不是過家家 說辦就能辦的\N{\rENG}A wedding doesn't just plan itself overnight, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:13.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,彩排就和正式儀式一模一樣\N{\rENG}And the rehearsal is just like the real thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.18,0:20:15.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,只是可以穿舒服點的鞋子\N{\rENG}only with comfortable shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.12,0:20:17.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,你們這位婚禮策劃可真夠可以的\N{\rENG}This wedding planner of yours is something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:20.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,真沒想到安多利人會這麼注重細節\N{\rENG}Never thought of Andorians as being so detail-oriented.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:24.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,你們兩個 就像太空艙裡的兩顆豆子\N{\rENG}You two, you're like two peas in a space pod.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.44,0:20:25.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,太登對啦\N{\rENG}So delightful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:27.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,那就先從蛋糕開始吧\N{\rENG}Let's start with the cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:29.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,等等 羅傑去哪裡了\N{\rENG}Wait, uh, where's Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.30,0:20:31.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,我覺得我們應該等等伴郎吧\N{\rENG}I feel like we should probably wait for my best man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.30,0:20:32.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,我來了\N{\rENG}I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:33.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,來了\N{\rENG}I am here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.06,0:20:35.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,我還帶來了蛋糕\N{\rENG}And I have the cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:35.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\rENG}Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:37.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,新鮮出爐 可香了\N{\rENG}Oh, yeah. Very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:39.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,克莉絲汀 我可以和你聊一下\N{\rENG}Christine, I couldn't just chat...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:41.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,稍後吧 科爾比先生\N{\rENG}Uh, later, Mr. Korby.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:42.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,是博士\N{\rENG}Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.36,0:20:43.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,叫我科爾比博士\N{\rENG}Dr. Korby.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.92,0:20:44.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rENG}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:46.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,其實我還有一個特別的伴郎任務\N{\rENG}Actually, I have a special best man task
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.96,0:20:47.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,專門需要你\N{\rENG}just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.71,0:20:50.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,你能在那邊等我一會兒嗎\N{\rENG}Could you wait for me way over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.42,0:20:52.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,越快越好\N{\rENG}Quick as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.14,0:20:56.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,真聽話\N{\rENG}Good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:57.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,那麼 史波克先生\N{\rENG}Now, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:20:59.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,我知道你想舉辦一場地球人風格的婚禮\N{\rENG}I know you wanted to embrace a human-type wedding,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:02.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,不過 要不要考慮混搭風\N{\rENG}but what about fusion style?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.44,0:21:05.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,我管它叫「人肯式」\N{\rENG}I call this "Hu-can."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.13,0:21:07.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,或者「瓦曼風」\N{\rENG}Or "Vul-man."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.90,0:21:09.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,嚐嚐看吧\N{\rENG}Just try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.26,0:21:17.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,你不喜歡嗎\N{\rENG}You hate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.14,0:21:23.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,我沒想到蛋糕會這麼辣 這麼咸\N{\rENG}I was not expecting cake with quite so much heat and brine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.76,0:21:38.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,再嚐一次 好不好\N{\rENG}Let's try that again, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.46,0:21:39.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,我來嚐一塊\N{\rENG}Oh, I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.38,0:21:43.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,史波克開玩笑的 蛋糕很美味啊\N{\rENG}Spock's joking, this is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.94,0:21:46.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,我能嚐到巧克力和\N{\rENG}Is it chocolate and, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.84,0:21:48.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,瓦肯帕克洛爾?\N{\rENG}Vulcan pahklor?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.06,0:21:49.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,沒錯 帕克洛爾\N{\rENG}Indeed, pahklor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.76,0:21:52.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,沒什麼能比帕克羅更能表達愛意了\N{\rENG}Nothing says love like pahklor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.00,0:21:55.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,我剛才一定是弄錯了\N{\rENG}I must've been mistaken before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.18,0:21:56.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,確實很好吃\N{\rENG}This is quite good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.32,0:21:58.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,不是很好 是完美\N{\rENG}Not just good but perfect,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.10,0:21:59.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,就像你們後面的婚禮一樣\N{\rENG}like your wedding is going to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.16,0:22:03.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,現在來討論一下編舞吧\N{\rENG}Let's talk about choreography.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.98,0:22:07.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,史波克 假設我們沒有婚斗儀式這個環節\N{\rENG}Spock, assuming we're not going to have a Kal-if-fee situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.98,0:22:07.58,Note,,0,0,0,,* 婚斗儀式是瓦肯習俗中兩個瓦肯男性為了女性交配對象決鬥至死的儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.58,0:22:09.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,你會在那邊的結婚聖壇\N{\rENG}I have you over on the altar
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.74,0:22:13.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,你的伴郎派克艦長就在前排\N{\rENG}and your best man Captain Pike in the front row
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.76,0:22:14.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,就在這裡\N{\rENG}just here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.80,0:22:16.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,喬瑟夫和烏娜呢\N{\rENG}Joseph and Una.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.48,0:22:21.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,你們簇擁著克莉絲汀 跳著華爾茲通過走道\N{\rENG}I see you waltzing Christine down the aisle
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.80,0:22:24.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,然後將她轉入史波克的臂彎\N{\rENG}and then spin her into Spock's arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.68,0:22:26.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,我可沒有練習這個\N{\rENG}I didn't practice that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.54,0:22:29.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,我為你準備了一個驚喜 害羞的新娘\N{\rENG}I have a surprise for you, my blushing bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.06,0:22:31.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,從地球的蒙福特州遠道而來\N{\rENG}Arrived all the way from Vermont, Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.84,0:22:33.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,今早收到的\N{\rENG}this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.90,0:22:35.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,我媽媽的手捧花?\N{\rENG}My mother's flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.50,0:22:38.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,她在婚禮後把手捧花保存起來了\N{\rENG}She had these preserved after her wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.54,0:22:50.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,噢不\N{\rENG}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:54.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,這些花看著是死透了啊\N{\rENG}Those flowers look dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.36,0:22:57.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,它們必須儲存在精確的2.7度下\N{\rENG}These were supposed to be stored at exactly 2.7 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.12,0:22:58.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,-說真的 -我很抱歉 克莉絲汀\N{\rENG}- I mean, the... - I'm so sorry, Christine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.86,0:23:00.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,有任何辦法能拯救這些花嗎\N{\rENG}Is there any way to salvage them?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.52,0:23:02.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,我的住艙裡有一個復水儀\N{\rENG}I-I have a rehydrator in my quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.80,0:23:03.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,聽我說一句吧\N{\rENG}I'll tell you what.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.48,0:23:05.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,可能它們只是需要出來透透氣\N{\rENG}Maybe they just need to breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.34,0:23:21.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,看吧\N{\rENG}I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.08,0:23:25.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,我的天 怎麼可能\N{\rENG}Oh, my God. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.17,0:23:27.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,還真可以啊 我簡直不敢相信\N{\rENG}It worked. I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.78,0:23:30.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,這就是為什麼我們要彩排\N{\rENG}This is why we have rehearsal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.20,0:23:32.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,既然解決了這個危機\N{\rENG}And with that avertation of the latest crisis,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.82,0:23:33.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,讓我們繼續吧\N{\rENG}let's continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.70,0:23:34.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,等你們兩個都站在聖壇\N{\rENG}With both at the altar,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.58,0:23:38.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,交換了戒指 大功告成\N{\rENG}we have the rings exchanged, and voilà.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.41,0:23:40.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,每個人都像特納蘭蝙蝠一樣開心\N{\rENG}Everyone's as happy as a Ternaran bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.88,0:23:43.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,克莉絲汀 我能和你說兩句嗎 拜託\N{\rENG}Uh, Christine, can we just chat for two seconds, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.88,0:23:45.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,很不巧 彩排剛剛結束\N{\rENG}Unfortunately, rehearsal has just finished,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.98,0:23:49.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,也就是說 查普爾護士 我必須要把你趕走\N{\rENG}which means, Nurse Chapel, I'm gonna have to scoop you away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.10,0:23:50.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,去最後試一次禮服\N{\rENG}for your final fitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.42,0:23:52.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,快點 該動身啦\N{\rENG}So quickly, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.03,0:23:55.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,拜託 別告訴你在婚禮上也準備穿著這件夾克\N{\rENG}Please tell me you're not gonna wear that jacket on the day,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.40,0:23:55.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,科布斯\N{\rENG}Korbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.16,0:24:06.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,嗨 你好嗎 最近過得怎麼樣 \N{\rENG}Hey, how are you? How're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.18,0:24:41.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,科爾比博士 你在做什麼\N{\rENG}Dr. Korby, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.85,0:24:45.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,我 呃\N{\rENG}I'm, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.90,0:24:48.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,想刪掉你的婚禮誓詞\N{\rENG}...trying to delete your vows.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.44,0:24:50.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,我就知道 蛋糕 還有手捧花\N{\rENG}I knew it. The cake, the flowers,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.76,0:24:52.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,你想要毀掉我們的婚禮\N{\rENG}you are trying to sabotage our wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.16,0:24:54.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊 你不能和克莉絲汀結婚\N{\rENG}Yeah, y-you can't marry Christine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.16,0:24:56.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,是因為你愛上她了嗎\N{\rENG}Are you in love with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.22,0:24:59.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,我是喜歡她 但這不是我這麼做的原因\N{\rENG}Yes. But that's not the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.30,0:25:00.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,不完全是\N{\rENG}Well, not entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.72,0:25:03.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,聽著 這場婚禮就不應該發生 明白嗎\N{\rENG}Look, this wedding is not supposed to happen, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.88,0:25:05.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不知道怎麼向你解釋\N{\rENG}Uh, I can't fully explain it,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.14,0:25:07.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是我們所在的現實被改變了\N{\rENG}but our reality has shifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.98,0:25:09.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,我覺得你該離開了 博士\N{\rENG}I think you should leave, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.12,0:25:09.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,聽我說完\N{\rENG}Just listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.90,0:25:11.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,克莉絲汀和我昨天才來到進取號\N{\rENG}Yesterday, Christine and I arrived on the Enterprise
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.98,0:25:13.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們是來參加聯邦建立百年紀念日的\N{\rENG}to attend the Federation's Centennial.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.24,0:25:15.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們特地把婚禮選在這個百年慶典的良辰吉日\N{\rENG}We specifically chose the centennial as our wedding day.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.31,0:25:17.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,不不不 我們就是為了紀念日才來到這裡的\N{\rENG}No, no, no, no. It is the reason we are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.84,0:25:20.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,到昨天為止 還沒有什麼婚禮\N{\rENG}As of yesterday, there was no wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.76,0:25:23.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,還沒有什{\fsp-50}麼{\fsp0}「你和查普爾護士彼此愛戀{\fsp-50}」{\fsp0}這一套\N{\rENG}There was no "you and Nurse Chapel."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.52,0:25:24.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,她明明和我在一起\N{\rENG}She and I were together.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.85,0:25:27.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,你是作為她的好朋友來參加婚禮的\N{\rENG}You arrived together because you are best friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.06,0:25:31.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,不 我們不是朋友 我們彼此相愛\N{\rENG}No, not as best friends, romantically we are together.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.18,0:25:34.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,只是似乎只有我一個人還記得這些事\N{\rENG}But I seem to be the only one here that remembers that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.36,0:25:36.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,三個月前 我向查普爾求婚\N{\rENG}I proposed to Christine three months ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.76,0:25:38.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,這一切都發生在她去參加你的研究項目之前\N{\rENG}before she embarked on her fellowship with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.68,0:25:40.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,我好不容易才拿到祖母的訂婚戒指\N{\rENG}I procured my grandmother's engagement ring--
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.32,0:25:41.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,你說的這些都沒發生過\N{\rENG}None of that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.54,0:25:43.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,為什麼只有我一個人記得\N{\rENG}Why am I the only one that remembers this?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.92,0:25:45.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,你們在她去進修之前就分手了\N{\rENG}You parted ways before the fellowship.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.88,0:25:48.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,確實 我第一次見到她的時候 她看起來很憂鬱\N{\rENG}And yeah, when I met her, at first, she was pretty gloomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.02,0:25:50.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,我理解 分手確實讓人難過\N{\rENG}I get it, endings are... are difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.14,0:25:51.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,博士 我認為你應該去醫務室檢查下腦子\N{\rENG}I think you should visit sickbay, Doc--
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.74,0:25:52.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\rENG}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.38,0:25:56.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,一開始 她確實只是學生\N{\rENG}At first, she was a fellow, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.24,0:25:58.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,但事情很快就發生了變化\N{\rENG}But she quickly became more.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.85,0:26:00.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,她逐漸趕上\N{\rENG}An equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.36,0:26:04.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,不久之後 她在瓦迪亞九星的發掘現場與我共事那會\N{\rENG}After a while, she was running the excavation site on Vadia Nine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.08,0:26:08.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,某天晚上 我們一起待到很晚\N{\rENG}And one night, we stayed late.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.86,0:26:12.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,我給她讀了一首聶魯達的詩\N{\rENG}And I read her a poem by Neruda.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.44,0:26:20.11,CHS,tag,0,0,0,,「我渴望你的嘴唇 你的嗓音 你的秀髮」\N{\rENG}"I crave your mouth, your voice, your hair."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.44,0:26:20.11,Note,tag,0,0,0,,* 出自聶努達《一百首愛的十四行詩·第十一首》
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.71,0:26:23.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,然後她\N{\rENG}And she, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.21,0:26:25.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,她吻了我\N{\rENG}She kissed me--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.09,0:26:39.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,哦 不好\N{\rENG}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.13,0:26:42.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,不好\N{\rENG}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.91,0:26:53.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,請冷靜 科爾比博士\N{\rENG}Please, Dr. Korby.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.44,0:26:54.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,我需要向你道歉\N{\rENG}I owe you an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.98,0:26:56.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,抱歉我打了你\N{\rENG}Yes, for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.00,0:26:57.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,而且 你說的對\N{\rENG}But also, you were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.95,0:26:59.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,現實確實被改變了\N{\rENG}Reality has been changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.55,0:27:01.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,一切都與原來不同\N{\rENG}None of this is how it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.25,0:27:02.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,你想起來了?\N{\rENG}So you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.66,0:27:03.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rENG}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.14,0:27:05.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,但我不確定是什麼原因造成的\N{\rENG}But I am not entirely sure why.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.06,0:27:06.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,你有把這件事告訴克莉絲汀嗎\N{\rENG}Have you tried telling Christine?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.25,0:27:08.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,我嘗試過 但是她沒有聽進去\N{\rENG}Yes, but she shut me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.10,0:27:09.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,如此廣泛的幻覺產生的原因\N{\rENG}I've considered several possible explanations
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.94,0:27:11.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,可能有以下幾個\N{\rENG}for this mass delusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.30,0:27:13.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,理論一 我們身處於一個平行宇宙中\N{\rENG}First, that this is an alternate dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.36,0:27:16.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,但我已經檢查了自身的相位變化 並無異常\N{\rENG}I've already checked myself for phase variance and found none.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.14,0:27:19.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,理論二 我們遭遇了某種環境致幻劑\N{\rENG}Second theory: exposure to an environmental hallucinogen.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.28,0:27:21.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,克莉絲汀和我同時到達進取號 所以\N{\rENG}Christine and I arrived at the same time, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.30,0:27:23.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,若這條理論成立 你也應當受到影響\N{\rENG}You would both be unaffected.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.28,0:27:24.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,說不定是某種外來病毒感染\N{\rENG}Alien virus?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.61,0:27:26.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,生物過濾器近期剛完成了升級 所以應該不是病毒造成的\N{\rENG}The bio-filters have been recently upgraded.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.36,0:27:29.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,或者是某種不確定場\N{\rENG}Perhaps an improbability field?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.36,0:27:33.65,Note,,0,0,0,,* 出自《奇異新世界》2x09「子空間狂想曲」
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.64,0:27:31.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們遇到過這種情況 導致我們一直在\N{\rENG}We once entered one that made us...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.74,0:27:33.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,歌唱\N{\rENG}sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.65,0:27:34.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,可能吧\N{\rENG}Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.72,0:27:36.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,我已經知曉了現狀\N{\rENG}Now that I am aware of the situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.25,0:27:39.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不會繼續參加這場婚禮儀式了\N{\rENG}I will obviously not proceed with the nuptials.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.29,0:27:44.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,你大概沒得選\N{\rENG}You may not have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.63,0:27:47.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,每當我試圖阻止這場婚禮\N{\rENG}Every time I've tried to stop this wedding,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.54,0:27:49.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,就會有東西妨礙我\N{\rENG}something has interfered.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.52,0:27:51.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,你是覺得這件事中\N{\rENG}You are suggesting the presence
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.37,0:27:52.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,有某種具有改變現實能力的\N{\rENG}of an advanced intelligent life-form
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.63,0:27:54.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,高級智慧生命體在干涉\N{\rENG}with reality-altering capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.54,0:27:55.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rENG}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.70,0:27:57.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,但為什麼只有你沒有受到影響\N{\rENG}But why leave you unaffected?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.50,0:27:58.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,這個嘛\N{\rENG}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.87,0:28:01.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,可能是我縝密的理性思維\N{\rENG}...my rigorous intellect may have
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.81,0:28:04.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,使我的頭腦免受幻覺的影響\N{\rENG}shielded my mind from the illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.08,0:28:07.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,博士\N{\rENG}Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.31,0:28:09.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果這個條件成立\N{\rENG}If one of our intellects could bestow immunity,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.60,0:28:11.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,我確信不受影響的一定不會是你\N{\rENG}I am confident it would not be yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.42,0:28:18.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,跟我來 我們可以去科學實驗室對整艘船進行掃描\N{\rENG}Come. We can use the science lab to scan the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.64,0:28:20.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果有異常能量出現 應該可以檢測到\N{\rENG}Any anomalous energy should be detectable.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.32,0:28:25.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,棒極了 又是那個討厭的安多利安人\N{\rENG}Great. Another Andorian annoyance.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.83,0:28:27.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,啊 終於找到你了\N{\rENG}Ah, there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.40,0:28:29.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,在這最幸福的婚禮的前夕\N{\rENG}Greetings and many felicitations
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.58,0:28:31.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,向你致以真誠的問候\N{\rENG}on this happiest of wedding eves.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.98,0:28:33.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,哦 科爾比先生\N{\rENG}Oh, Mr. Korby.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.32,0:28:33.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,是博士\N{\rENG}Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.76,0:28:35.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,怎麼哪兒都有你\N{\rENG}You really are everywhere, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.54,0:28:36.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,狗皮膏藥似的\N{\rENG}Bit like a rash.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.54,0:28:38.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,說到這個 婚禮那邊的其他賓客\N{\rENG}Speaking of which, the rest of the bridal party
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.94,0:28:40.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,正在享受面部護理\N{\rENG}are enjoying facials.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.22,0:28:42.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,你要不要也去體驗一下\N{\rENG}Perhaps you should join them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.02,0:28:43.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,你看起來有點呆\N{\rENG}You do look a little dull.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.42,0:28:44.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,是不是沒睡好\N{\rENG}Are you sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.26,0:28:46.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,黑眼圈這麼重 肯定是沒睡好\N{\rENG}The bags beneath your eyes say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.70,0:28:49.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,我親愛的新郎 你看這些衣服怎麼樣\N{\rENG}My darling groom, what do you think of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.76,0:28:51.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,這個顏色很襯你的瞳色\N{\rENG}The color really brings out your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.58,0:28:53.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,可以延後嗎 我現在有一些緊急事務需要處理\N{\rENG}Could this wait? I have urgent duties to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.86,0:28:54.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,別傻了\N{\rENG}Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.70,0:28:57.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,現在 你最重要的任務就是結婚\N{\rENG}Right now, your most important mission is matrimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.82,0:29:02.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,這件就可以了\N{\rENG}That one will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.02,0:29:03.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們得走了\N{\rENG}Come. We must go.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.44,0:29:04.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,說了是博士\N{\rENG}It's Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.22,0:29:07.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,哎呦 博士呢\N{\rENG}"It's Doctor."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.58,0:29:11.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,這實驗室挺不錯\N{\rENG}Nice lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.16,0:29:15.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,執行全艦掃描程序 這應該會耗費幾分鐘\N{\rENG}Initiating ship-wide scan now. It will take a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.18,0:29:18.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,我在想你是怎麼意識到這是一場幻覺的\N{\rENG}I was thinking about how it was that you became disillusioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.30,0:29:19.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,我揮出那一拳的那一瞬間\N{\rENG}At the moment I punched you,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.80,0:29:21.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,就好像我腦海中迷霧消散了\N{\rENG}it was as if a fog in my mind lifted,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.88,0:29:24.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,然後我就知道了\N{\rENG}and I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.68,0:29:28.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,也許是腎上腺素和皮質醇的突然爆發造成的\N{\rENG}Perhaps it was the sudden burst of adrenaline and cortisol that did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.34,0:29:29.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,也有可能是因為\N{\rENG}It is also possible that whatever power
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.73,0:29:31.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,當我們直面真相的時候\N{\rENG}is creating this false reality cannot be maintained
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.73,0:29:33.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,這場錯誤的幻覺就無法維持下去了\N{\rENG}when so directly confronted with the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.06,0:29:35.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,無論如何 我們都需要找到辦法\N{\rENG}Regardless, we must find a way
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.94,0:29:37.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,告知艦長當前的情況\N{\rENG}to communicate the situation to the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.30,0:29:39.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,那祝你好運了\N{\rENG}Good luck with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.18,0:29:40.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,終於找到你了\N{\rENG}There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.62,0:29:42.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,你怎麼不在自己的房間待著\N{\rENG}You were supposed to meet me in your quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.54,0:29:44.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,不管這是什麼 我都不能喝\N{\rENG}Whatever this is, I cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.06,0:29:46.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,山姆 你帶來的是什麼\N{\rENG}Sam! What do we have here?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.08,0:29:49.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,來選明天婚宴主桌要上的葡萄酒吧\N{\rENG}These are the wine selections for the head table tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.68,0:29:57.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,請你認真聽我說 柯克上尉\N{\rENG}Listen to me very carefully, Lieutenant Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.62,0:29:59.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,進取號停泊在一號星站是為了\N{\rENG}Enterprise came to Starbase One
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.36,0:30:01.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,慶祝聯邦建立百年紀念日\N{\rENG}to celebrate the Federation Centennial.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.50,0:30:03.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,而不是婚禮\N{\rENG}Not a wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.36,0:30:05.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,查普爾護士早已和我分手\N{\rENG}Nurse Chapel and I are no longer a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.83,0:30:07.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們不會結婚\N{\rENG}We are not getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.96,0:30:11.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,你正處於一種未知現象的影響下\N{\rENG}You are suffering from an unknown phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.00,0:30:13.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,很有可能我們遭到了某種襲擊\N{\rENG}It is possible we are all under attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.01,0:30:16.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,我懂的\N{\rENG}I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.63,0:30:19.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,我理解你 史波克 你想打退堂鼓\N{\rENG}I get it, Spock, you have cold feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.84,0:30:21.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,這太正常了 你聽我說\N{\rENG}It's totally normal, look--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.10,0:30:21.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,給我一拳\N{\rENG}Punch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.80,0:30:22.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,啥\N{\rENG}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.67,0:30:27.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,我揍你幹什麼\N{\rENG}I'm not gonna punch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.32,0:30:28.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,你做事馬虎\N{\rENG}You are sloppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.84,0:30:30.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,不如你的兄弟聰明\N{\rENG}Less intelligent than your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.82,0:30:33.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,沒有人喜歡你的鬍子\N{\rENG}No one likes your mustache.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.46,0:30:40.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,而且你對酒的品味很差\N{\rENG}And you have terrible taste in wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.97,0:30:48.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果我在你婚禮前夕給你打得眼眶烏青\N{\rENG}If I gave you a black eye the day before your wedding,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.01,0:30:49.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,克莉絲汀會殺了我的\N{\rENG}Christine would kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.98,0:30:51.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,掃描完成\N{\rENG}Scan complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.01,0:30:53.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,當前並未檢測到異常能量讀數\N{\rENG}There are no anomalous energy readings present.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.25,0:30:56.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,就要霞多麗葡萄酒吧\N{\rENG}Perhaps the chardonnay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.48,0:31:00.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,艦長 我們需要報告緊急情況\N{\rENG}Sir, we have an urgent situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.58,0:31:02.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,我非常清楚 少校\N{\rENG}I am aware, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.13,0:31:07.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,喝了這個就好了\N{\rENG}And there. Fixed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.83,0:31:11.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,史波克先生 歡迎來到你的單身派對\N{\rENG}Mr. Spock, welcome to your bachelor party.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.94,0:31:13.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,-嘿 -史波克喲\N{\rENG}- Hey. - Spock-o!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.86,0:31:15.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,我準備了所有你喜歡的東西\N{\rENG}Spock! I prepared all of your favorites.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.58,0:31:17.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,瓦肯巨貝 普克塔\N{\rENG}Jumbo mollusk, Pok-tar, and 
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.58,0:31:17.82,Note,tag,0,0,0,,* 分別出自《深空九號》2x06 以及《進取號》1x08
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.82,0:31:19.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,還有看看我找到了什麼\N{\rENG}look what I found.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.34,0:31:20.87,CHS,tag,0,0,0,,魯土格\N{\rENG}Lutrog.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.87,0:31:23.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,還有為我們其他人準備的\N{\rENG}And something imbibable for the rest of us:
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.68,0:31:24.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,蜥蜴白蘭地\N{\rENG}Saurian brandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.58,0:31:28.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,哦 說實話 我不怎麼喝酒\N{\rENG}Oh, honestly, I'm not really much of a drinker.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.10,0:31:29.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,我幾乎碰不了那東西\N{\rENG}I hardly touch the stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.78,0:31:31.05,CHS,,0,0,0,,我覺得吧 按照習俗\N{\rENG}I believe tradition dictates
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.05,0:31:33.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,準新郎在踏入婚姻墳墓之前 得先說段祝酒詞\N{\rENG}the groom-to-be give us a toast before he walks the plank.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.69,0:31:35.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,對啊 演講\N{\rENG}Yes, speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.58,0:31:38.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,來吧 史波克先生\N{\rENG}Come on, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.72,0:31:42.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們所在的現實遭到了改變\N{\rENG}Our reality has been changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.26,0:31:45.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,查普爾護士早已和我分手\N{\rENG}Nurse Chapel and I are not together.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.44,0:31:47.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,她現在和科爾比博士戀愛了\N{\rENG}She is in love with Dr. Korby,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.28,0:31:49.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,但現在只有我和他記得這件事\N{\rENG}and only he and I remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.34,0:31:57.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,敬史波克 世界上最幸運的人\N{\rENG}To Spock, the luckiest man in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.81,0:31:59.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,對 敬史波克\N{\rENG}Yes, to Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.04,0:32:00.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,-史波克先生 -乾杯\N{\rENG}- Mr. Spock. - Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.58,0:32:05.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,艦長 進取號正在遭受大規模幻覺影響\N{\rENG}Captain, Enterprise is experiencing a mass delusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.15,0:32:06.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,我就說吧 他又打退堂鼓了\N{\rENG}I told you. Cold feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.48,0:32:07.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,我沒有在打鼓 多謝關心\N{\rENG}My feet are perfectly warm, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.04,0:32:10.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,我是認真的\N{\rENG}This is serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.06,0:32:12.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,放輕鬆 史波克\N{\rENG}Relax, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.32,0:32:14.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,我知道這對你來說很難\N{\rENG}Which I know is difficult for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.30,0:32:17.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以才要請你吃魯土格\N{\rENG}That's why the Lutrog.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.40,0:32:20.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,要慢點吃啊\N{\rENG}Careful with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.02,0:32:23.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,到目前為止 情況似乎已經很清楚\N{\rENG}It seems clear by now that being confronted 
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.72,0:32:26.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,僅僅告知大家真相併不足以打破這種魔咒\N{\rENG}with the truth is not enough to break the spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.11,0:32:28.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,這就只剩下情感反應這一途徑了\N{\rENG}Which leaves us with emotional response.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.38,0:32:29.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,但我們已經觀察到了各種各樣的情感\N{\rENG}But we have seen a range of emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.44,0:32:31.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,卻沒有一種能驅散這種幻覺\N{\rENG}and yet none dispel the delusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.08,0:32:38.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,生氣 憤怒 這是最強烈的一種情感了\N{\rENG}Anger, rage, it's one of the most powerful emotions there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.40,0:32:42.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,或許需要另一種同樣強烈的情感\N{\rENG}Perhaps another equally powerful emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.46,0:32:44.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,比如什麼\N{\rENG}Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.12,0:32:45.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,愛\N{\rENG}Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.44,0:32:48.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,對了史波克 我差點忘了\N{\rENG}Mr. Spock, I almost forgot, 
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.16,0:32:50.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,婚禮策劃人請你評價一下座位安排表如何\N{\rENG}the wedding planner asked you to weigh in on the seating arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.60,0:32:53.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,不介意的話 請看看第八排\N{\rENG}Take a look at row eight, if you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.24,0:32:54.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,呃 艦長\N{\rENG}Uh, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.68,0:32:57.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,一共有多少人受邀出席了這場婚禮\N{\rENG}How many guests are invited to the wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.04,0:33:00.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,全體船員以及 107名登記的來賓\N{\rENG}All the crew and, uh, 107 registered guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.76,0:33:01.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,謝了\N{\rENG}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.30,0:33:05.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,計算機 當前進取號上\N{\rENG}Computer, how many individuals
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.46,0:33:06.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,除了船員和登記的來賓\N{\rENG}are currently aboard the Enterprise
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.66,0:33:09.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,還有多少其他個體的存在\N{\rENG}besides crew and registered guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.48,0:33:11.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,一個\N{\rENG}One.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.24,0:33:13.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,婚禮有個不速之客\N{\rENG}We have a wedding crasher.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.68,0:33:15.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,就藏在我們眼皮底下\N{\rENG}Hiding in plain sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.04,0:33:16.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,計算機 定位該個體的位置\N{\rENG}Computer, locate that individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.36,0:33:21.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,符合條件的個體位於左舷餐廳\N{\rENG}The individual fitting that description is in the Port Galley.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.72,0:33:26.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,史波克 你要去哪\N{\rENG}Spock, where you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.26,0:33:27.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,待會還要去唱卡拉OK呢\N{\rENG}We're gonna do karaoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.20,0:33:31.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,噢 科爾比先生 史波克先生\N{\rENG}Oh, Mr. Korby, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.24,0:33:32.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,你們不是應該在參加單身派對嗎\N{\rENG}Shouldn't you be at your bachelor party?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.98,0:33:36.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,我正在準備招待會的特調飲品\N{\rENG}I'm working on a specialty drink for the reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.28,0:33:38.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,二位覺得石榴汁怎麼樣\N{\rENG}How do we feel about pomegranate?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.18,0:33:40.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不需要一場狂歡宴\N{\rENG}I do not need a bacchanal.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.19,0:33:41.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,那你就該好好睡個美容覺\N{\rENG}Then you should get your beauty rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.70,0:33:43.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,我現在也睡不著\N{\rENG}I do not need to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.62,0:33:45.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,那就數瑪梵入睡吧\N{\rENG}Count tribbles, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.52,0:33:47.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,你 你就是那個實體\N{\rENG}You. You are the entity.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.32,0:33:49.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,哦 史波克先生\N{\rENG}Oh, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.02,0:33:51.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,你那瓦肯式幽默感每次都能逗到我\N{\rENG}Your Vulcan sense of humor gets me every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.56,0:33:54.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,還記得嗎 我是你的婚禮策劃人呀\N{\rENG}I'm your wedding planner, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.00,0:33:57.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,你旋轉著走進我的辦公室 滿心沉醉在愛意中\N{\rENG}You twirled into my office, drunk on love,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.06,0:34:00.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,夢想著一場既夢幻又讓人喜不自勝的婚禮\N{\rENG}wishing for a wedding day full of magic and unspeakable joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.98,0:34:01.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,夢想?\N{\rENG}A wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.52,0:34:04.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,那一晚 就在這個地方\N{\rENG}That night, here in the Port Galley,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.12,0:34:05.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,你那會也是酒保\N{\rENG}you were the bartender then, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.36,0:34:08.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,我希望我和克莉絲汀之間的情況能有所不同\N{\rENG}I wished things could be different with Christine.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.52,0:34:10.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,而你讓它成為了現實\N{\rENG}And you made it so.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.20,0:34:12.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,不用謝\N{\rENG}You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.14,0:34:13.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,這不重要\N{\rENG}It does not matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.54,0:34:15.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們不會進行這場婚禮\N{\rENG}We are not going through with the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.34,0:34:17.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,你必須將其復原\N{\rENG}You have to fix this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.40,0:34:19.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,你不能就這樣操控人們的思想\N{\rENG}You can't just control people's minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.59,0:34:21.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,我愛怎麼樣就怎麼樣\N{\rENG}I can do anything I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.54,0:34:23.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,我是個婚禮策劃師\N{\rENG}I am a wedding planner.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.10,0:34:34.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,此外 我不喜歡被別人破壞我的計劃\N{\rENG}And I do not like it when people ruin my plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.04,0:34:42.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,醒一醒 史波克先生\N{\rENG}Wakey wakey, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.96,0:34:44.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,今天是你的大喜之日\N{\rENG}It's your big day.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.44,0:34:46.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,你不能強迫我繼續演這場戲\N{\rENG}You cannot force me to continue this charade.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.08,0:34:48.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,哎呦 真的假的\N{\rENG}Can't I, though? 
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.65,0:34:49.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,要是你惹我生氣的話\N{\rENG}Do you know what would happen
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.54,0:34:51.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,不用想大家會是什麼樣的下場吧\N{\rENG}to everyone if you made me mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.14,0:34:53.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,我甚至都想像不出來下場\N{\rENG}I don't think I can even imagine it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.23,0:34:59.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,哇 快看\N{\rENG}Well, look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.58,0:35:01.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,我的小型瓦肯生態皿\N{\rENG}My own little Vulcan terrarium.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.73,0:35:03.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,我的朋友們肯定羨慕壞了\N{\rENG}My friends will be so jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.87,0:35:09.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,現在知道要乖乖聽話了嗎\N{\rENG}I do hope you'll play along now, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.18,0:35:16.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,我聽到婚禮的鐘聲敲響了\N{\rENG}I can hear the wedding bells.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.82,0:35:42.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,哎喲 看看你 真是帥氣啊\N{\rENG}Ah! Look at you, you look great.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.50,0:35:45.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以婚禮都應該在沙灘上進行\N{\rENG}All weddings should be on the beach
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.37,0:35:47.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,而且所有人都應該穿著短褲\N{\rENG}and everyone should be in shorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.76,0:35:48.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rENG}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.80,0:35:55.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,我一直在找你\N{\rENG}I have been searching for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.02,0:35:58.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,他逼著我做伴郎\N{\rENG}He's made me the maid of honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.00,0:35:59.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,他說如果我不乖乖照做的話\N{\rENG}And he says if I don't play along,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.32,0:36:01.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,他要把我們都發配到玉米地裡去\N{\rENG}he's gonna wish us all to a cornfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.32,0:36:01.38,Note,,0,0,0,,* 發配到玉米地是《陰陽魔界》裡的梗 見該劇集的3x08
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.38,0:36:03.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不明白玉米地有什麼特殊的含義\N{\rENG}I do not understand the significance of this wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.58,0:36:06.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,這是個梗 算了\N{\rENG}It's from a... Doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.06,0:36:07.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,他的意思是把我們都從現實中抹除\N{\rENG}He's talking about wiping us from all of existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.96,0:36:10.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,是的 他也這樣威脅我了\N{\rENG}Yes, he made this threat to me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.18,0:36:11.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,你得把這件事做完\N{\rENG}You're gonna have to go through with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.90,0:36:14.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,就是 可能唯一的解決辦法\N{\rENG}Just... Maybe that's the only way to end it,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.90,0:36:16.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,就是順著他來\N{\rENG}play his game.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.64,0:36:19.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,史波克 到時候了\N{\rENG}It's time, Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.61,0:36:21.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,咱們讓你成婚吧\N{\rENG}Let's get you married.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.32,0:37:32.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,請大家落座\N{\rENG}Please be seated.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.75,0:37:39.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,今日能齊聚一堂\N{\rENG}What a delight
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.82,0:37:42.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,共同見證如此特別的時刻\N{\rENG} to be gathered here today to celebrate 
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.20,0:37:43.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,真是令人欣喜\N{\rENG}something so special,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.82,0:37:47.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,一種比最快的星艦更強大的力量\N{\rENG}a force more powerful than the fastest starship.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.54,0:37:50.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,人類稱之為愛\N{\rENG}Humans call it love,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.26,0:37:53.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,而我聽說 愛可以戰勝一切\N{\rENG}and I'm told love can conquer all things.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.78,0:37:54.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,克莉絲汀\N{\rENG}Christine--
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.64,0:37:56.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,噓 早了\N{\rENG}Shh. Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.46,0:38:03.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,你們都有準備誓詞吧\N{\rENG}Do you both have your vows?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.28,0:38:04.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\rENG}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.76,0:38:06.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rENG}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.52,0:38:08.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,我反對\N{\rENG}I object.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.42,0:38:09.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,還沒到那個環節呢\N{\rENG}We're not there yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.30,0:38:10.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,羅傑 你在幹什麼\N{\rENG}Roger, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.24,0:38:12.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,克莉絲汀 你必須停下\N{\rENG}Christine, you have to stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.64,0:38:13.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,該停下的是你\N{\rENG}You stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.74,0:38:16.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,你不能就這樣改變別人的感受\N{\rENG}You can't just make people feel things
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.08,0:38:17.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,改變別人的真情實感\N{\rENG}that they don't really feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.84,0:38:18.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,夠了\N{\rENG}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.06,0:38:30.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,請繼續 史波克先生\N{\rENG}Please, continue, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.28,0:38:42.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,人類詩人聶魯達曾寫道\N{\rENG}The human poet Neruda wrote,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.60,0:38:46.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,「我渴望你的嘴唇 你的嗓音\N{\rENG}"I crave your mouth, your voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.14,0:38:48.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,你的秀髮\N{\rENG}"your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.39,0:38:50.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不說話 不吃喝\N{\rENG}"Silent and starving,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.18,0:38:52.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,遊蕩在街頭巷尾\N{\rENG}"I prowl through the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.39,0:38:54.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,麵包無法果腹\N{\rENG}"Bread does not nourish me,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.90,0:38:56.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,黎明只會令我發狂\N{\rENG}"dawn disrupts me,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.30,0:38:58.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,整日裡\N{\rENG}"all day
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.64,0:39:01.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,我追尋你腳步流水般的韻姿」\N{\rENG}I hunt for the liquid measure of your steps."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.48,0:39:06.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,這就是愛你的感覺 克莉絲汀\N{\rENG}This is what it is like to love you, Christine.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.06,0:39:09.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,而值得你的愛的人\N{\rENG}And the person worthy of your love,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.80,0:39:12.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,必須要勇敢\N{\rENG}they must be courageous.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.10,0:39:15.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,不能沉溺迷失\N{\rENG}They cannot be drowning.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.38,0:39:16.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,不能搖擺不定\N{\rENG}They cannot be unsure
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.72,0:39:19.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,也不能任由自己的情感風暴裹挾\N{\rENG}or at the mercy of their own emotional storms.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.68,0:39:23.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,他必須是你靈魂的港灣\N{\rENG}They must be a safe harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.69,0:39:27.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,要能為你守住一方寧靜\N{\rENG}They must have the ability to hold space for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.83,0:39:29.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,去看到你\N{\rENG}To see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.30,0:39:30.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,最真實的你\N{\rENG}Just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.17,0:39:35.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,他必須聽得見你未曾出口的呼喚\N{\rENG}They must be able to hear your unuttered call.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.21,0:39:43.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,要能夠把一切都交予你\N{\rENG}They must be able to give you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.08,0:39:49.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,必須能把\N{\rENG}They must offer you the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.28,0:39:53.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,日月星辰\N{\rENG}and the sun and the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.52,0:39:55.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,都一併贈予你\N{\rENG}all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.62,0:40:02.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,我並不清楚你母親的生日是哪天\N{\rENG}I did not know when it was your mother's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.20,0:40:05.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,我沒告訴你\N{\rENG}I didn't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.47,0:40:07.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,這不是誰的錯\N{\rENG}It's no one's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.12,0:40:13.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,這不對 史波克\N{\rENG}This is wrong, Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.38,0:40:20.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們不應該結婚\N{\rENG}We're not supposed to be getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.85,0:40:22.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,對\N{\rENG}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.02,0:40:24.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們不應該\N{\rENG}We are not.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.72,0:40:26.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,你倆應該呀\N{\rENG}Yes, you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.66,0:40:28.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,羅傑\N{\rENG}Roger...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.66,0:40:31.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,羅傑\N{\rENG}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.52,0:40:33.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,呃 不 他是隻狗\N{\rENG}Well, no, he's a dog,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.03,0:40:34.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以 不行\N{\rENG}so... No!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.86,0:40:36.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,我絕對不允許\N{\rENG}No, no, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.62,0:40:38.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,夠了\N{\rENG}That is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.10,0:40:39.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,大家都得死\N{\rENG}Everybody dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.88,0:40:42.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,就從這條狗開始\N{\rENG}And I'm starting with the dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.14,0:40:43.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,你離他遠點\N{\rENG}You keep away from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.46,0:40:45.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,準備好迎接你們的末日吧\N{\rENG}Prepare for a cavalcade of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.70,0:40:48.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,你們今晚誰也別想吃到婚禮蛋糕\N{\rENG}No one gets a wedding cake slice tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.10,0:40:49.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,你死定了\N{\rENG}You're going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.20,0:40:50.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,你要死翹翹了\N{\rENG}You'll be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.30,0:40:52.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,然後你 戴著皇冠的 腦子裡裝的啥\N{\rENG}And you with the crown, what were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.34,0:40:54.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,是想搶新娘風頭嗎\N{\rENG}Tried to outshine the bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.08,0:40:56.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,還有你們幾個藍臉的 你們明知道我穿著藍色衣服\N{\rENG}And you blue faces, you could see I was in blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.92,0:40:58.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,你們哪來的膽\N{\rENG}How dare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.32,0:40:59.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,去死吧你\N{\rENG}Death to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.56,0:41:00.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,還有後面那個\N{\rENG}And you at the back
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.44,0:41:01.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,連張嘴都沒有\N{\rENG}with no mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.60,0:41:02.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,就是你\N{\rENG}Yes, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.82,0:41:05.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,但說實話 我挺喜歡的\N{\rENG}Actually, that's... I like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.56,0:41:07.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,就放過你吧\N{\rENG}You can, you can live.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.24,0:41:09.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,這是什麼情況\N{\rENG}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.24,0:41:10.38,Note,,0,0,0,,* 配音演員同時也是Q的演員 主創也確認這裡就是Q
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.40,0:41:16.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,不是現在 老爹\N{\rENG}Not now, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.66,0:41:18.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,唉 你惹的麻煩也夠多了吧\N{\rENG}Oh, you've made enough of a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.74,0:41:20.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,拜託別在這丟人現眼的了\N{\rENG}Please, let's not make a scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.40,0:41:22.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,噢 天哪\N{\rENG}Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.98,0:41:24.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,克莉絲汀\N{\rENG}Christine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.04,0:41:27.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,但他們一點都不配合誒\N{\rENG}But they're not playing along.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.02,0:41:28.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,他們壓根不聽我的\N{\rENG}They're not listening to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.20,0:41:30.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,然而你也不聽我的話\N{\rENG}And you are not listening to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.02,0:41:34.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,還用我再向你說明一遍不聽話的下場嗎\N{\rENG}Shall I show you once more what the consequence is for disobedience?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.36,0:41:35.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,不用\N{\rENG}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.00,0:41:38.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,我會聽話的 我保證\N{\rENG}I'll be good, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.79,0:41:40.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,等等 你還只是個孩子嗎\N{\rENG}Wait, you're a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.64,0:41:42.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,很小的孩子\N{\rENG}A very young one.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.08,0:41:44.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,按照地球時間算才八千歲\N{\rENG}Only 8,000 of your Earth years.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.06,0:41:45.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,是八千零二十歲 爹\N{\rENG}8,020, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.56,0:41:47.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,該走了\N{\rENG}It's time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.58,0:41:48.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,我還不想走\N{\rENG}I don't want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.68,0:41:50.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,等一下 在你離開之前\N{\rENG}Wait, before you leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.04,0:41:53.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,我想知道你為什麼這麼做\N{\rENG}...might I ask why?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.48,0:41:55.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,這個嘛\N{\rENG}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.46,0:41:56.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,看那傢伙\N{\rENG}Look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.66,0:42:00.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,我發現他在老家那邊挖來挖去的\N{\rENG}I spotted him digging in the dirt on the old homeworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.62,0:42:04.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,他實在是完美 一個又帥又聰明的人\N{\rENG}He's just so handsome and smart and perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.46,0:42:05.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,看到他就火大\N{\rENG}It's just annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.82,0:42:08.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,是 這確實合乎邏輯\N{\rENG}Yes, that does make perfect sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.56,0:42:09.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\rENG}Oy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.42,0:42:11.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,現在 讓其他人恢復正常\N{\rENG}Now, free the rest of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.74,0:42:12.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rENG}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.76,0:42:23.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,拜拜囉\N{\rENG}Tallyho.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.58,0:42:25.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,玩你們玩的很開心\N{\rENG}You've all been lots of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.82,0:42:52.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,好了大家 沒事了 沒事了\N{\rENG}Okay, everybody, all right, all right,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.06,0:42:53.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,大家聽我說下\N{\rENG}all right, okay, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.46,0:42:57.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,那個 呃 剛剛那件事很奇怪\N{\rENG}That was, uh, that-that-that... that was strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.22,0:42:59.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,這場什麼婚禮的共同幻覺\N{\rENG}A shared delusion about a wedding
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.11,0:43:00.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,可真是個新鮮事 是吧\N{\rENG}is a new one, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.49,0:43:04.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧 呃 聯邦日\N{\rENG}Okay... Uh, Federation Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.21,0:43:06.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,在2161年 星聯的創始種族們\N{\rENG}2161, the, uh, founding species
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.55,0:43:10.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,聚集在一起創立了 呃 星際聯邦\N{\rENG}came together to create, uh, the Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.82,0:43:12.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,呃 主要是為了回應\N{\rENG}Um, largely in response
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.32,0:43:15.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們與其他外星種族{\fsp-50}的{\fsp0}「友好互動」\N{\rENG}to our interactions with other foreign species.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.19,0:43:17.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,這期間發生了一些非常尷尬的事情\N{\rENG}Some of them very awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.46,0:43:19.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,呃 所以用一種\N{\rENG}Uh, so it's only fitting
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.76,0:43:22.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,與其同樣尷尬的活動\N{\rENG}that-that our-our centennial be marked
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.36,0:43:25.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,來紀念聯邦成立百年\N{\rENG}by a-a-a similar awkward,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.76,0:43:28.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,挺合適的\N{\rENG}uh, interaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.92,0:43:33.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,總之 今天酒吧暢飲\N{\rENG}And the bar is open.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.92,0:43:47.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,這看著好好喝\N{\rENG}Those look incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.34,0:43:44.62,Note,,0,0,0,,* 這裡的酒保是埃多斯人 這也是該種族首次在真人劇集中出現 之前均是在動畫劇集中出現
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.52,0:43:50.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,可以給你調一杯 但這是阿拉妮黑麥威士忌\N{\rENG}I'll make you one, but it's Alanni Rye.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.64,0:43:53.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,它會在你的食道和它下面的東西\N{\rENG}It will burn a hole through your esophagus
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.46,0:43:56.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,全部蝕穿個洞出來\N{\rENG}and whatever is below your esophagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.42,0:43:58.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,地板可能也難逃一劫\N{\rENG}And maybe the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.26,0:43:59.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,那就請給我兩品脫吉尼斯黑啤吧\N{\rENG}Two pints of Guinness, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.12,0:44:02.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,這個也許穩妥點\N{\rENG}Probably a safer bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.24,0:44:03.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,你是進取號上的醫官嗎\N{\rENG}Are you the doctor from the Enterprise?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.76,0:44:06.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,約瑟夫·姆'本加\N{\rENG}Joseph M'Benga.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.46,0:44:22.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,我有點想念你戴著花冠的樣子了\N{\rENG}You know, I kind of miss the flower crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.24,0:44:23.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,-是嗎 -是啊\N{\rENG}- Oh, yeah? - Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.50,0:44:25.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,我也有點想念\N{\rENG}I kind of miss the big green veil thing
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.26,0:44:27.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,你穿的那件綠色婚紗了\N{\rENG}you had going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.02,0:44:28.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,可以說 不是每個女孩都夢想著\N{\rENG}Well, I can tell you it is not every girl's dream
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.63,0:44:31.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,被一個宇宙騙子利用情感玩過家家\N{\rENG}to have a cosmic trickster play dress-up dolls
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.98,0:44:33.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,擺布她的情緒\N{\rENG}with her emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.94,0:44:36.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,還讓她嫁錯了人\N{\rENG}and make her marry the wrong man.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.40,0:44:38.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,這過去的四十八個小時\N{\rENG}The last 48 hours have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.92,0:44:40.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,羅傑\N{\rENG}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.11,0:44:42.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\rENG}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.64,0:44:46.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,我也一樣\N{\rENG}Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.60,0:44:49.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,好了 我們就去跳舞吧\N{\rENG}Now, let's go dance 
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.50,0:44:52.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,以後誰再也別提這事了\N{\rENG}and never talk about this ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.12,0:44:53.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,成交\N{\rENG}Deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.78,0:45:04.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,你和我想的一樣嗎\N{\rENG}You thinking what I'm thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.02,0:45:06.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,但我們得處理得好才行\N{\rENG}If we play our cards right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.73,0:45:08.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,噢 我們只是想和你說\N{\rENG}Oh, we were just saying that an artist
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.27,0:45:09.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,這麼才華橫溢的藝術家\N{\rENG}with such prodigious skills
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.77,0:45:11.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,待在星站上真是大材小用了\N{\rENG}shouldn't be confined to a starbase.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.09,0:45:15.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果你的意思是想給我一個星艦上的崗位\N{\rENG}If you're offering me a job on a starship,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.85,0:45:17.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,我樂意效勞\N{\rENG}my answer is yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.85,0:45:20.05,CHS,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\rENG}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.15,0:45:22.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 幸會幸會 - 謝謝\N{\rENG}- Pleasure meeting you. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.08,0:45:24.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,我剛剛與星際艦隊公關部的負責人\N{\rENG}I just had a very interesting conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.70,0:45:26.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,進行了一次有趣的對談\N{\rENG}with the Chancellor of Starfleet's Public Relations.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.45,0:45:27.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,是嗎\N{\rENG}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.18,0:45:30.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,他們有意向讓我拍一部星際艦隊的紀錄片電影\N{\rENG}They may commission a feature-length documentary of Starfleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.40,0:45:32.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,那個負責人挺喜歡我\N{\rENG}Well, the Chancellor likes me,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.01,0:45:33.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,我可以跟他多美言幾句\N{\rENG}so I'll put in a good word.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.79,0:45:36.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,你知道的 只要能煩到艾麗卡\N{\rENG}You know, anything to annoy Erica.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.60,0:45:39.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們要去煩艾麗卡嗎\N{\rENG}Shall we annoy Erica?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.48,0:45:41.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,敬煩人的艾麗卡\N{\rENG}To annoying Erica.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.44,0:46:05.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,你剛剛的演講可真精彩\N{\rENG}That was a beautiful speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.23,0:46:09.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,是的 大概吧\N{\rENG}Yes. I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.13,0:46:13.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,愛有萬千形態 史波克先生\N{\rENG}Love comes in all forms, Mr. Spock,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.17,0:46:16.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,而你給了她屬於你的那份\N{\rENG}and you gave her yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.69,0:46:20.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,我並不後悔\N{\rENG}And I have no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.64,0:46:26.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,但努力到頭來 還是付諸東流了\N{\rENG}Still, it is a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.08,0:46:27.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,什麼努力\N{\rENG}What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.28,0:46:28.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,你最近的時間都花在學習跳舞上了\N{\rENG}Well, you spent all this time learning to dance,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.88,0:46:29.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,結果你現在光坐著\N{\rENG}and now you're just
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.98,0:46:31.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,啥都不用\N{\rENG}sitting on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.15,0:46:34.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,畢竟 你的肩膀位置都已經\N{\rENG}After all, your shoulder placement
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.79,0:46:37.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,精確測量好了 不是嗎\N{\rENG}has been measured precisely, has it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.19,0:46:40.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果我沒記錯的話\N{\rENG}If I'm not mistaken,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.06,0:46:42.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,你說不需要精確測量\N{\rENG}I am not supposed to measure them.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.36,0:46:43.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,我該讓它們順其自然\N{\rENG}I am supposed to let them flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.03,0:46:47.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,上尉\N{\rENG}Lieutenant...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.03,0:46:48.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,你是在邀請我共舞嗎\N{\rENG}are you asking me to dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.97,0:46:50.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}吉特巴舞\N{\rENG}{\i1}♪ Jitterbug ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.94,0:46:53.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}吉特巴舞\N{\rENG}{\i1}♪ Jitterbug ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.77,0:46:54.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,你來上\N{\rENG}It's all you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.91,0:46:56.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}吉特巴舞\N{\rENG}{\i1}♪ Jitterbug ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.17,0:46:59.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}吉特巴舞\N{\rENG}{\i1}♪ Jitterbug ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.72,0:47:03.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}你讓我的小心臟砰砰直跳\N{\rENG}{\i1}♪ You put the boom boom into my heart ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.61,0:47:07.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}當你的愛降臨時 你讓我的靈魂飛上雲霄\N{\rENG}{\i1}♪ You send my soul sky high when your loving starts ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.04,0:47:09.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我滿腦子跳著吉特巴舞\N{\rENG}{\i1}♪ Jitterbug into my brain ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.69,0:47:12.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}邦邦邦 我成了抖腿狂魔\N{\rENG}{\i1}♪ Goes a bang-bang-bang till my feet do the same ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.93,0:47:15.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}但是有東西左右著你的心\N{\rENG}{\i1}♪ But something's bugging me, something ain't right ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.90,0:47:19.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我最好的朋友告訴我你昨晚都幹了啥\N{\rENG}{\i1}♪ My best friend told me what you did last night ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.00,0:47:21.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}你把我撇下 讓我獨自入夢\N{\rENG}{\i1}♪ Left me sleeping in my bed ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.40,0:47:23.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我還幻想著\N{\rENG}{\i1}♪ I was dreaming ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.10,0:47:25.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}本應和你如影隨形\N{\rENG}{\i1}♪ But I should've been with you instead ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.41,0:47:28.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}走之前記得叫醒我\N{\rENG}{\i1}♪ Wake me up before you go-go ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.38,0:47:31.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}突然消失會讓我的心神不寧\N{\rENG}{\i1}♪ Don't leave me hanging on like a yo-yo ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.37,0:47:34.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}走之前記得叫醒我\N{\rENG}{\i1}♪ Wake me up before you go-go ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.32,0:47:37.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}因為我不想錯過你高漲的一瞬\N{\rENG}{\i1}♪ I don't want to miss it when you hit that high ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.26,0:47:40.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}走之前一定記得叫醒我\N{\rENG}{\i1}♪ Wake me up before you go-go ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.22,0:47:43.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}因為我不想形單影隻\N{\rENG}{\i1}♪ 'Cause I'm not planning on going solo ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.20,0:47:46.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}走之前記得叫醒我\N{\rENG}{\i1}♪ Wake me up before you go-go ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.97,0:47:50.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}今晚帶我去狂舞吧\N{\rENG}{\i1}♪ Take me dancing tonight ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.18,0:47:57.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fad(0,1500)}我想好好瘋一把\N{\rENG}{\i1}♪ I want to hit that high. ♪
